ired up LeBron James, the \\\"King\\\" wearing shiny golden sneakers to mark the occasion.\", \"from\": 515, \"to\": 714, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 524, \"end\": 530, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.989341296664006, \"rank\": 0.010355735741184558, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 581, \"end\": 589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.733617485536507, \"rank\": 0.36297336150793374, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 638, \"end\": 650, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LeBron James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am just living in the moment,\\\" said 39-year-old James, the NBA's all-time leading scorer.\", \"from\": 716, \"to\": 808, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 767, \"end\": 772, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 0.9999999979781933, \"rank\": 1.2833204132750089e-09, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}, {\"begin\": 778, \"end\": 781, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.150661010033573e-21, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am super humbled that I can still play this game.\", \"from\": 809, \"to\": 861, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Play it at a high level.\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 888, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Play with 11 other great players with a great coaching staff and then and go out and do it for our country.\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 998, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was a great moment.\\\"\", \"from\": 1000, \"to\": 1024, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The result was the same as three years ago in the Tokyo Olympics gold-medal game, but for the French, this loss cut a little deeper coming on home hardwood in front of a captivated nation.\", \"from\": 1026, \"to\": 1214, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1120, \"end\": 1126, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.989341296664006, \"rank\": 0.010355735741184558, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's their incredible talent that ended up marking the difference,\\\" said France coach Vincent Collet.\", \"from\": 1216, \"to\": 1318, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1290, \"end\": 1296, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8840822182584412, \"rank\": 0.1299572845965341, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1303, \"end\": 1317, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vincent_Collet\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vincent Collet\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vincent_Collet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vincent_Collet\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a final against the Americans, in Paris, you can say it as much as you want, each player has his emotions, we tried to use them but it wasn't possible here.\\\"\", \"from\": 1319, \"to\": 1482, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1359, \"end\": 1364, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.788436892738256e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Steph Curry would finish with 24 points, all coming from three-pointers on an 8-of-12 clip, while a defiant, scowling James had 14 points, 10 assists, and 6 rebounds.\", \"from\": 1484, \"to\": 1650, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1484, \"end\": 1495, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_Curry\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Steph Curry\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_Curry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_Curry\"}, {\"begin\": 1602, \"end\": 1607, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 0.9999999979781933, \"rank\": 1.2833204132750089e-09, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kevin Durant and Devin Booker also fired 15 points each\\u00a0for the superstar-studded American squad.\", \"from\": 1652, \"to\": 1749, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1658, \"end\": 1664, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.827812882654007e-17, \"text\": \"Durant\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\"}, {\"begin\": 1669, \"end\": 1681, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Devin_Booker\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.739830018959692e-33, \"text\": \"Devin Booker\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Devin_Booker\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Devin_Booker\"}, {\"begin\": 1734, \"end\": 1742, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.733617485536507, \"rank\": 0.36297336150793374, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just downstream from Notre Dame cathedral on the banks of the Seine, the French faithful, including President Emmanuel Macron, gathered at the Bercy like pilgrims to Lourdes believing anything is possible, and so it seemed, until the final moments of an enthralling final.\", \"from\": 1751, \"to\": 2023, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1813, \"end\": 1818, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 9.280227702894834e-13, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}, {\"begin\": 1824, \"end\": 1830, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.989341296664006, \"rank\": 0.010355735741184558, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 1861, \"end\": 1876, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emmanuel Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 1894, \"end\": 1899, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Accor_Arena\", \"score\": 0.8271107579834328, \"rank\": 0.20902792080485