_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While the Americans celebrated, there were tears from a shattered French team that Wembanyama said wasready to leave blood on courtin their quest for gold.\", \"from\": 2850, \"to\": 3005, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2916, \"end\": 2922, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.989341296664006, \"rank\": 0.010355735741184558, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wembanyama, the first French player taken No.\", \"from\": 3007, \"to\": 3052, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3029, \"end\": 3035, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.989341296664006, \"rank\": 0.010355735741184558, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"1 overall in the NBA draft, covered his face and wept before searching out his mother, who comforted her 7-foot-3 son.\", \"from\": 3053, \"to\": 3171, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3070, \"end\": 3073, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.150661010033573e-21, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 20-year-old power forward finished with a game high 26- points playing with flair and passion that marked him out as a future leader of the French squad.\", \"from\": 3173, \"to\": 3330, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3317, \"end\": 3329, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9555913905503837, \"rank\": 0.04647237429623781, \"text\": \"French squad\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http:/